e of the demented pederast,  Humbert Humbert , who is the narrator in his novel Lolita (  1955 )."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Humbert de Salins was born about 1060, in Salins, Seine-et-Marne, France, his father, Gaucher de Salins II, was 31 and his mother, Béatrix de Dreux, was 26. He married Aremburge before 1088, in Europe. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter. He died in 1149, at the age of 90."},"et":{"um 1060–1149":"umbes 1060–1149","1060–1149":"1060–1149","–Female":"Surnud","1088–1175":"1088–1175","1125–Female":"1125–Surnud","1030–1100":"1030–1100","1035–1084":"1035–1084","um 1060":"umbes 1060","1149":"1149","1125":"1125","Aft 1100":"pärast 1100","before 1088":"enne 1088","1035":"1035","1100":"1100","1088":"1088","1175":"1175","1030":"1030","1084":"1084","1060":"1060","Salins, Seine Et Marne, France":"Salins, Seine-et-Marne, Prantsusmaa","Salins, France":"Salin, Landes, Aquitaine, Prantsusmaa","Europe":"Europe"},"fi":{"um 1060–1149":"noin 1060–1149","1060–1149":"1060–1149","–Female":"Kuollut","1088–1175":"1088–1175","1125–Female":"1125–Kuollut","1030–1100":"1030–1100","1035–1084":"1035–1084","um 1060":"noin 1060","1149":"1149","1125":"1125","Aft 1100":"1100 jälkeen","before 1088":"ennen vuotta 1088","1035":"1035","1100":"1100","1088":"1088","1175":"1175","1030":"1030","1084":"1084","1060":"1060","Salins, Seine Et Marne, France":"Salins, Seine-et-Marne, Ranska","Salins, France":"Salin, Landes, Aquitaine, Ranska","Europe":"Europe"},"fr":{"um 1060–1149":"environ 1060–1149","1060–1149":"1060–1149","–Female":"Décédée","1088–1175":"1088–1175","1125–Female":"1125–Décédée","1030–1100":"1030–1100","1035–1084":"1035–1084","um 1060":"environ 1060","1149":"1149","1125":"1125","Aft 1100":"après 1100","before 1088":"avant 1088","1035":"1035","1100":"1100","1088":"1088","1175":"1175","1030":"1030","1084":"1084","1060":"1060","Salins, Seine Et Marne, France":"Salins, Seine-et-Marne, France","Salins, France":"Salin, Landes, Aquitaine, France","Europ